<C>__{ruth }
<D>__{nexterior}
<A>__{the mau mau's run onto the stage, yelling and screaming. they are all fired up, in fact several fire their 9mm's into the ceiling. angle two shot delacroix and sloan.}
<C>__{sloan}
<D>__{this is the group i was telling you about.}
<C>__{delacroix}
<D>__{which one is your brother?}
<C>__{sloan}
<D>__{the big one.}
<B>__{close on}
<A>__{ruth.}
<C>__{ruth}
<D>__{let's get started here.}
<B>__{angle on stage}
<A>__{big black preens around on the stage.}
<C>__{big black}
<D>__{the mau mau's are up in dis place. that's right, the mau mau's.}
<C>__{delacroix }
<D>__{what's your name?}
<C>__{big black}
<D>__{my righteous name is big black.}
<C>__{delacroix }
